-- Brit Group valued at $1.6 billion in IPO - source
-- 
-- Thu Mar 27, 2014 12:56PM EDT
-- None



LONDON, March 27 (Reuters) - Netherlands-based insurer Brit Group [IPO-BRIT.L] is to price its London IPO at 240 pence per share, a source said on Thursday, valuing the company at 960 million pounds ($1.6 billion).

The Lloyd's of London underwriter is selling a 25 percent stake of 100 million shares. The price is at the top of its narrowed range of 235-240 pence a share.